# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  SignFlow AI — Backend Environment Variables
#  Copy this file to .env for local development
#  For Railway: set these in Dashboard → Your Service → Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── Database ─────────────────────────────────────────
# REQUIRED — MongoDB Atlas connection string.
# DO NOT use mongodb://localhost:27017 in production.
# Railway cannot reach your local machine!
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://<user>:<password>@<cluster>.mongodb.net/<dbname>?retryWrites=true&w=majority

# ─── Authentication ────────────────────────────────────
# REQUIRED — generate with: openssl rand -hex 64
JWT_SECRET=your_super_secret_jwt_key_min_32_chars
REFRESH_SECRET=your_refresh_token_secret_min_32_chars

# ─── Email (Resend) ────────────────────────────────────
# REQUIRED for email delivery
RESEND_API_KEY=re_your_resend_api_key_here
# Your verified custom domain sender (must be verified in Resend dashboard)
FROM_EMAIL=signflow@abhinavsai.com

# ─── Frontend URL ─────────────────────────────────────
# REQUIRED — used for email link generation and CORS
# Production: https://signflow.abhinavsai.com
# Local dev:  http://localhost:5177
FRONTEND_URL=https://signflow.abhinavsai.com

# ─── Backend URL ──────────────────────────────────────
# Used for OAuth redirects (set to your Railway deployment URL)
# Production: https://signflow-api.up.railway.app
# Local dev:  http://localhost:5000
BACKEND_URL=https://signflow-api.up.railway.app

# ─── Server ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Railway injects PORT automatically. Set NODE_ENV for production.
NODE_ENV=production
# PORT is set automatically by Railway — do NOT set this manually on Railway

# ─── Stripe (Optional) ────────────────────────────────
# Required only for real billing integration
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_your_stripe_key_here
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_your_webhook_secret_here
